### 机场贵宾厅预约权益核验规则计算 API 服务
### 基础地址: http://localhost:3000/api

### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### ========== 会员权益 CRUD ==========

### 获取所有会员权益
GET http://localhost:3000/api/member-benefits

### 获取单个会员权益
GET http://localhost:3000/api/member-benefits/1

### 创建会员权益
POST http://localhost:3000/api/member-benefits
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 张伟

{
  "code": "VIP-TEST-001",
  "name": "测试机场贵宾厅年度权益-钻石卡",
  "status": "draft",
  "responsible_person": "张伟",
  "member_level": "diamond",
  "remaining_quota": 10,
  "total_quota": 12,
  "effective_date": "2025-01-01",
  "expiry_date": "2025-12-31",
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2025-TEST",
  "remark": "测试创建"
}

### 更新会员权益
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/member-benefits/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 张伟

{
  "remaining_quota": 7,
  "remark": "更新剩余额度"
}

### 删除会员权益
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/member-benefits/1
X-Operator: 张伟

### ========== 预约记录 CRUD ==========

### 获取所有预约记录
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservations

### 获取单个预约记录
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/1

### 创建预约记录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 李娜

{
  "code": "RSV-TEST-001",
  "name": "测试机场贵宾厅预约-XX0001",
  "status": "draft",
  "responsible_person": "李娜",
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_slot_id": 1,
  "companion_count": 1,
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2025-TEST",
  "remark": "测试预约"
}

### 更新预约记录
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 李娜

{
  "companion_count": 2,
  "remark": "增加同行人"
}

### 删除预约记录
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/2
X-Operator: 李娜

### ========== 预约记录批量导入预检 ==========

### 批量导入预约记录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/batch-import
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 批量导入员

{
  "items": [
    {
      "code": "RSV-BATCH-001",
      "name": "批量导入预约-首都机场CA1234",
      "responsible_person": "张伟",
      "member_benefit_id": 1,
      "flight_slot_id": 1,
      "companion_count": 0,
      "batch_no": "BATCH-IMPORT-001",
      "remark": "批量导入测试"
    },
    {
      "code": "RSV-BATCH-002",
      "name": "批量导入预约-浦东机场MU5678",
      "responsible_person": "李娜",
      "member_benefit_id": 2,
      "flight_slot_id": 2,
      "companion_count": 1,
      "batch_no": "BATCH-IMPORT-001",
      "remark": "批量导入测试"
    },
    {
      "code": "RSV-BATCH-INVALID",
      "name": "",
      "responsible_person": "",
      "member_benefit_id": 999,
      "flight_slot_id": 999,
      "remark": "这条应该校验失败"
    }
  ]
}

### ========== 航班时段 CRUD ==========

### 获取所有航班时段
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots

### 获取活跃航班时段
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots/active

### 获取已归档航班时段
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots/archived

### 获取单个航班时段
GET http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots/1

### 创建航班时段
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 赵敏

{
  "code": "FLT-TEST-001",
  "name": "测试航班时段-XX0001",
  "status": "draft",
  "responsible_person": "赵敏",
  "airport_code": "CTU",
  "flight_number": "XX0001",
  "departure_time": "2026-05-25T10:00:00",
  "arrival_time": "2026-05-25T13:00:00",
  "capacity": 20,
  "used_count": 0,
  "is_archived": 0,
  "snapshot_data": null,
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2025-TEST",
  "remark": "测试航班时段"
}

### 归档航班时段
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots/1/archive
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 赵敏

### 创建航班时段快照
POST http://localhost:3000/api/flight-slots/1/snapshot
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 赵敏

### ========== 核验权益资格 ==========

### 核验预约的权益资格
POST http://localhost:3000/api/verifications
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 核验员

{
  "reservation_id": 1
}

### 获取所有核验结果
GET http://localhost:3000/api/verifications

### 获取单个核验结果
GET http://localhost:3000/api/verifications/1

### ========== 候补名单 ==========

### 获取所有候补名单
GET http://localhost:3000/api/waitlists

### 创建候补名单条目
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waitlists
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 孙丽

{
  "code": "WTL-TEST-001",
  "name": "测试候补条目",
  "status": "waiting",
  "responsible_person": "孙丽",
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_slot_id": 1,
  "wait_start_time": "2026-05-24T20:00:00",
  "priority_score": 75.0,
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2025-TEST",
  "remark": "测试候补"
}

### 安排候补入场
POST http://localhost:3000/api/waitlists/arrange
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 候补管理员

{
  "flight_slot_id": 1
}

### 获取航班时段的候补等待列表
GET http://localhost:3000/api/waitlists/flight-slot/1

### ========== 入场优先级计算 ==========

### 计算会员在指定航班的入场优先级
POST http://localhost:3000/api/priority/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 优先级计算员

{
  "member_benefit_id": 1,
  "flight_slot_id": 1
}

### 直接计算优先级（不关联数据库实体）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/priority/calculate-raw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "member_level": "diamond",
  "remaining_quota": 8,
  "total_quota": 12,
  "departure_time": "2026-05-25T08:00:00",
  "wait_start_time": "2026-05-24T20:00:00"
}

### 重新计算航班时段所有候补的优先级
POST http://localhost:3000/api/priority/recalculate/1
X-Operator: 优先级计算员

### ========== 权益过期异常判定 ==========

### 检查过期权益并生成异常事件
POST http://localhost:3000/api/exceptions/check
X-Operator: 异常检查员

### 获取所有异常事件
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exceptions

### 获取待处理异常事件
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exceptions/pending

### 获取单个异常事件
GET http://localhost:3000/api/exceptions/1

### 处理异常事件
POST http://localhost:3000/api/exceptions/1/handle
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 处理员A

{
  "handler": "处理员A",
  "action": "handling"
}

### ========== 统计聚合 ==========

### 权益核验通过率统计（按日）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics/verification-rate?group_by=day

### 权益核验通过率统计（按批次）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics/verification-rate?group_by=batch

### 权益核验通过率统计（按责任人）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics/verification-rate?group_by=responsible_person

### 候补转入率统计
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics/waitlist-transfer-rate?group_by=day

### 入场使用率统计
GET http://localhost:3000/api/statistics/usage-rate?group_by=day

### ========== 状态流转 ==========

### 执行状态流转
POST http://localhost:3000/api/status-flow
Content-Type: application/json
X-Operator: 流转操作员

{
  "entity_type": "member_benefit",
  "entity_id": 5,
  "from_status": "draft",
  "to_status": "pending_review",
  "action": "submit",
  "responsible_person": "陈静",
  "reject_reason": null,
  "batch_no": "BATCH-2025-SZX"
}

### 查询状态流转记录
GET http://localhost:3000/api/status-flow?entity_type=member_benefit&entity_id=1

### 获取允许的状态流转
GET http://localhost:3000/api/status-flow/allowed-transitions?current_status=draft

### ========== 审计日志 ==========

### 查询审计日志（分页）
GET http://localhost:3000/api/audit-logs?limit=20&offset=0

### 按实体类型查询审计日志
GET http://localhost:3000/api/audit-logs?entity_type=member_benefit

### 按操作人查询审计日志
GET http://localhost:3000/api/audit-logs?operator=张伟

### ========== Seed 重置 ==========

### 重置数据库并重新导入 seed 数据
POST http://localhost:3000/api/seed/reset
